{
  "stem": "26672.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then went to school, [NON-ENGLISH] school, came home for lunch, met my sis-- my sis, met by my sister, gave me some lunch, and take me on to the next stage of my education.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So didn't have much time to-- for play, but we always found [? time, ?] with boys we always found time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure we found time to play, mostly winters, skating on our hills, or sliding down some little hill, and making up, um, slates or whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sure we [INAUDIBLE] doing the same thing as boys do today, maybe more modern way today you got computers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they sit in those and watch television.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We never had television or radio.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember having radio at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, um, with whom did you play?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Boys in the cheder.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This the year of the school, nah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they were mostly non-Jews anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Jewish boys I used to meet in the cheder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to play together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how close we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sure we were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In those days, most families were close, rich or poor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Family was something that we could learn today, from today, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember, um, when he came into power.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't, I was too young to remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only time I remember when this came about was, um, when war broke out, and the planes kept coming over our town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people are running to hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to come down so low, you could see the pilots, almost their eyeballs and shooting at the people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's my first recollection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure I must have done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sure, but who exactly individually, I-- I wouldn't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
